  "stem": "<p>The expression 5 &middot; <sup>7</sup>&radic;(2<sup>7</sup><i>x</i><sup>21</sup>) &middot; <sup>9</sup>&radic;(3<sup>9</sup><i>x</i>) is equivalent to <i>a</i><i>x</i><sup><i>b</i></sup>, where <i>a</i> and <i>b</i> are positive constants and <i>x</i> &gt; 1. What is the value of <i>a</i> + <i>b</i>?</p>",
